title: Coriander Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Take-out, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vietnamese style cuisine. You start with choice of preparation (banh mi sandwich, rice bowl, noodle salad, or lettuce wraps), then add choice of protein (tofu is only option), then the garnish. Also has vegetarian egg rolls, papaya salad, and vegan spring rolls. Uses local produce when possible, and uses a locally made tofu. Free Wi-Fi and reading section.
